"," classes"," can"," also"," provide"," students"," with"," the"," opportunity"," to"," take"," courses"," from"," reputable"," institutions",","," further"," increasing"," the"," likelihood"," of"," graduation",".","\n\n","Online"," classes"," can"," also"," provide"," students"," with"," a"," sense"," of"," community"," and"," support","."," While"," online"," classes"," lack"," the"," face","-","to","-","face"," interaction"," of"," traditional"," classrooms",","," they"," offer"," alternative"," ways"," for"," students"," to"," connect"," with"," their"," peers"," and"," instructors","."," For"," example",","," online"," discussions",","," video"," conferencing",","," and"," social"," media"," can"," provide"," students"," with"," opportunities"," to"," engage"," with"," their"," classmates"," and"," instructors"," in"," a"," virtual"," setting","."," This"," sense"," of"," community"," can"," be"," crucial"," for"," students"," who"," may"," feel"," isolated"," in"," a"," traditional"," classroom"," setting",".","\n\n","However",","," online"," classes"," are"," not"," without"," their"," challenges","."," One"," of"," the"," primary"," concerns"," with"," online"," learning"," is"," the"," potential"," for"," decreased"," student"," engagement"," and"," motivation","."," Without"," the"," structure"," and"," accountability"," of"," a"," traditional"," classroom",","," some"," students"," may"," struggle"," to"," stay"," on"," track"," with"," their"," coursework","."," Online"," classes"," require"," a"," high"," level"," of"," self","-","discipline"," and"," time"," management"," skills",","," which"," may"," be"," challenging"," for"," some"," students",".","\n\n","To"," address"," these"," challenges",","," it"," is"," crucial"," to"," provide"," adequate"," support"," and"," resources"," for"," online"," students","."," This"," support"," can"," include"," access"," to"," academic"," advising",","," technical"," assistance",","," and"," mental"," health"," resources","."," Online"," instructors"," should"," also"," provide"," regular"," feedback"," and"," communication"," with"," their"," students"," to"," ensure"," they"," are"," on"," track"," with"," their"," coursework",".","\n\n","In"," conclusion",","," online"," classes"," offer"," numerous"," benefits"," for"," students"," who"," are"," unable"," to"," attend"," traditional"," classes"," due"," to"," personal"," issues"," or"," other"," reasons","."," Online"," classes"," provide"," a"," more"," personalized"," learning"," experience",","," offer"," convenience"," and"," flexibility",","," and"," can"," increase"," graduation"," rates","."," However",","," it"," is"," crucial"," to"," provide"," adequate"," support"," and"," resources"," for"," online"," students"," to"," address"," the"," challenges"," of"," online"," learning","."," With"," the"," right"," support"," and"," resources",","," online"," classes"," can"," provide"," a"," viable"," alternative"," to"," traditional"," classroom"," learning","."],"sub_source":"outfox","model":"mixtral-8x7b","label":1}